channel.description: The latest CVEs for opensuse -- openbuildservice

item.title: CVE-2018-12467|2024-09-16T18:34:59.508Z -- opensuse -- openbuildservice
item.description: Authorized users of the openbuildservice before 2.9.4 could delete packages by using a malicious request against projects having the OBS:InitializeDevelPackage attribute, a similar issue to CVE-2018-7689.

item.title: CVE-2011-3178|2024-09-16T20:47:59.849Z -- opensuse -- openbuildservice
item.description: In the web ui of the openbuildservice before 2.3.0 a code injection of the project rebuildtimes statistics could be used by authorized attackers to execute shellcode.
